1.切换到root账户：
sudo su

2 安装 MySQL 5
apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client
系统会提示你设置密码

3 安装 Nginx
apt-get install nginx
启动Nginx服务：
service nginx start
去浏览器看一下：http://localhost

5 设置 nginx ,修改文件：
vi /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
修改一些主机的基本配置

虚拟主机配置文件修改：
vi /etc/nginx/sites-available/blog
修改代码如下面的显示：
server {
    listen 80;

    root /workspace/web/robin/blog/;
    index index.html index.htm index.php entry.php;

    # Make site accessible from http://localhost/
    server_name blog.robin.com.cn;

    set $rewrite yes;
    location ~ ^/favicon\.ico$ {
        root    /workspace/web/robin/blog/
    }

    if ( $request_uri ~* ^/(data|public|assets|crossdomain\.xml|index\.php|favicon\.ico) ) {
        set $rewrite no;
    }


    if ($rewrite ~* yes) {
        rewrite ^/(.*) /index.php/$1 last;
    }

    location ~ /(data|public|assets|crossdomain\.xml)
    {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }

    location / {
        fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php5-fpm.sock;
        fastcgi_index index.php;
        include fastcgi_params;
    }

    location /doc/ {
            alias /usr/share/doc/;
            autoindex on;
            allow 127.0.0.1;
            allow ::1;
            deny all;
    }
    # Only for nginx-naxsi used with nginx-naxsi-ui : process denied requests
    #location /RequestDenied {
    #       proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8080;    
    #}

    #error_page 404 /404.html;

    # redirect server error pages to the static page /50x.html
    #
    #error_page 500 502 503 504 /50x.html;
    #location = /50x.html {
    #       root /usr/share/nginx/html;
    #}

    # pass the PHP scripts to FastCGI server listening on 127.0.0.1:9000
    #
    location ~ \.php$ {
            fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
            # NOTE: You should have "cgi.fix_pathinfo = 0;" in php.ini

            # With php5-cgi alone:
            #fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;
            # With php5-fpm:
            fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php5-fpm.sock;
            fastcgi_index index.php;
            include fastcgi_params;
    }

    # deny access to .htaccess files, if Apache's document root
    # concurs with nginx's one
    #
    #location ~ /\.ht {
    #       deny all;
    #}
}
重新加载nginx:
service nginx restart

4 安装 PHP5
apt-get install php5-fpm

安装好后执行 php -i

注意：此处如果报错，直接安装缺少组件即可

扩展：

查询PHP模块：
apt-cache search php5

例如输入下面安装你要的模块：
apt-get install php5-mysql php5-curl php5-gd php5-intl php-pear php5-imagick php5-imap php5-mcrypt php5-memcache php5-ming php5-ps php5-pspell php5-recode php5-snmp php5-sqlite php5-tidy php5-xmlrpc php5-xsl php5-redis
安装完毕之后重启php5-fpm
service php5-fpm restart
